  "id": "RAW_6a9f8614",
  "title": "今日开源（2025-12-31）：腾讯推出 Hunyuan-Motion 1.0，DiT 架构+流匹配技术，高效生成 3D 动作方案",
  "url": "https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MzkyMzcwMDIyMQ==&mid=2247501166&idx=1&sn=35a06fc0aab95907108635263ace015e",
  "date": "2025-12-31 10:30:00",
  "author": "机器之心SOTA模型",
  "siteName": "机器之心SOTA模型",
  "content": "<html>\n <head></head>\n <body>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"text-indent: 0px;text-align: center;\"><strong style=\"text-align: center;font-weight: bold;font-size: 22px;letter-spacing: 0.034em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"text-align: center;font-weight: bold;font-size: 22px;letter-spacing: 0.034em;\">🏆基座模型</span></strong></p>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"><strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">①项目：Hunyuan-Motion 1.0</span></span></strong></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img js_insertlocalimg\" data-ratio=\"0.31203703703703706\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" type=\"block\" data-imgfileid=\"100017508\" data-aistatus=\"1\" style=\"height: auto !important;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=e6363994&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FGU2ibjU7TDkyiaTmZl1iccqPLJBSU7mvbeibia6icEVtb2VXkz8EWnO4sgkKOG8ox8laqWDg2HlKlPLLtib4fzY3uE4CQ%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: bold;\">★Hunyuan-Motion 1.0是一系列基于Diffusion Transformer (DiT)和流匹配的文本到3D人类动作生成模型。</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: normal;\">该项目允许开发者从简单的文本提示生成基于</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: bold;\">骨架</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: normal;\">的3D角色动画，并可直接集成到各种3D动画管道中。该模型系列首次将</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: bold;\">基于DiT</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: normal;\">的文本到动作模型扩展到十亿参数级别，在指令跟随能力和动作质量上实现了显著提升。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"outline:0px;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;margin-bottom:8px;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"padding:4px;outline:0px;color:rgb(255, 104, 39);letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;text-align:start;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">☆一键收藏：</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"outline:0px;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;margin-bottom:8px;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"padding:4px;outline:0px;color:rgb(255, 104, 39);letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;text-align:start;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><a href=\"https://sota.jiqizhixin.com/project/hunyuan-motion-1-0\" target=\"_blank\">https://sota.jiqizhixin.com/project/hunyuan-motion-1-0</a></span></span></p>\n  <p><strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">②项目：Yuan3.0-Flash</span></span></strong></p>\n  <p><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.5018518518518519\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" data-width=\"1160\" data-height=\"582\" data-imgfileid=\"100017497\" data-aistatus=\"1\" style=\"height: auto !important;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=b5a1b489&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FGU2ibjU7TDkyiaTmZl1iccqPLJBSU7mvbeibWhNW0Go5Rtf0LFS0XaOadHB3OP62BdYQp7SG9MNYTictj8nwYIGR8iaA%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: bold;\">★Yuan3.0-Flash是由YuanLab.ai团队开发的一个40B参数的多模态基础模型，采用Mixture of Experts (MoE)架构，每次推理仅激活约3.7B参数。</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: normal;\">通过创新的</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: bold;\">增强学习训练方法（RAPO）</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: normal;\">，显著减少推理时的token消耗，同时提高推理准确性，探索了“大模型小计算”的创新路径。该模型特别针对企业级应用场景进行了深度优化，支持文本、图像、表格、文档等多模态输入，具备128K的上下文长度支持。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"outline:0px;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;margin-bottom:8px;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"padding:4px;outline:0px;color:rgb(255, 104, 39);letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;text-align:start;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">☆一键收藏：</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"outline:0px;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;margin-bottom:8px;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"padding:4px;outline:0px;color:rgb(255, 104, 39);letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;text-align:start;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><a href=\"https://sota.jiqizhixin.com/project/yuan3-0-flash\" target=\"_blank\">https://sota.jiqizhixin.com/project/yuan3-0-flash</a></span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;font-size: 22px;letter-spacing: 0.034em;\">🛠️ 框架平台、必备工具</span></p>\n  <p><strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">①项目：NVIDIA NeMo</span></span></strong></p>\n  <p><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.7203703703703703\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" data-width=\"1164\" data-height=\"838\" data-imgfileid=\"100017499\" data-aistatus=\"1\" style=\"height: auto !important;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=c077f5ff&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FGU2ibjU7TDkyiaTmZl1iccqPLJBSU7mvbeibD0j6HBUHMySvKrdAX6BN8TIOmP88DouHwziahAChKctMI2INody02YA%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: bold;\">★NVIDIA NeMo是一个可扩展的生成式AI框架，专为研究人员和开发人员设计，支持大语言模型、多模态和语音AI（自动语音识别和文本转语音）。</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: normal;\">该框架提供了丰富的工具和资源，帮助用户在不同的AI任务中实现高效的模型训练和部署。NeMo框架的最新版本引入了对Hugging Face模型的支持，并提供了多种新模型和优化方案，旨在提升AI模型的性能和易用性。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"outline:0px;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;margin-bottom:8px;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"padding:4px;outline:0px;color:rgb(255, 104, 39);letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;text-align:start;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">☆一键收藏：</span></span></p>\n  <p><span style=\"padding:4px;outline:0px;color:rgb(255, 104, 39);letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"padding:4px;outline:0px;color:rgb(255, 104, 39);letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;text-align:start;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><a href=\"https://sota.jiqizhixin.com/project/nvidia-nemo\" target=\"_blank\">https://sota.jiqizhixin.com/project/nvidia-nemo</a></span></span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"text-align: center;font-weight: bold;font-size: 22px;letter-spacing: 0.034em;\">🤖 Agent 开发</span></p>\n  <p><strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">①项目：MAI-UI</span></span></strong></p>\n  <p><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.4\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" data-width=\"1160\" data-height=\"464\" data-imgfileid=\"100017501\" data-aistatus=\"1\" style=\"height: auto !important;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=aad885c2&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FGU2ibjU7TDkyiaTmZl1iccqPLJBSU7mvbeibEVYCaoMOicFrXcZZBDIZvS3GibZ0xmx5keqUZxu67pdUx74HyDdjXicjQ%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: bold;\">★MAI-UI是一组面向真实世界的基础GUI Agent，旨在革新下一代人机交互。</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: normal;\">项目涵盖多种规模的模型，包括2B、8B、32B和235B-A22B变体。MAI-UI通过</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: bold;\">自我进化</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: normal;\">的数据管道、设备云协作系统和在线强化学习框架，解决了Agent用户交互缺乏、UI操作限制、部署架构缺失和动态环境脆弱性等挑战。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"outline:0px;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;margin-bottom:8px;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"padding:4px;outline:0px;color:rgb(255, 104, 39);letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;text-align:start;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">☆一键收藏：</span></span></p>\n  <p><span style=\"padding:4px;outline:0px;color:rgb(255, 104, 39);letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"padding:4px;outline:0px;color:rgb(255, 104, 39);letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;text-align:start;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><a href=\"https://sota.jiqizhixin.com/project/mai-ui\" target=\"_blank\">https://sota.jiqizhixin.com/project/mai-ui</a></span></span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"text-align: center;font-weight: bold;font-size: 22px;letter-spacing: 0.034em;\">⚙️ Robotics 开发</span></p>\n  <p><strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">①项目：RoboTracer</span></span></strong></p>\n  <p><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.35648148148148145\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" data-width=\"1162\" data-height=\"414\" data-imgfileid=\"100017503\" data-aistatus=\"1\" style=\"height: auto !important;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=c5363e1d&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FGU2ibjU7TDkyiaTmZl1iccqPLJBSU7mvbeibentypIGaV7P3TIKBFLtI3Ac2o3H7iaJ9iaRc1puPhibvEJZLTmJI5ScpQ%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: bold;\">★RoboTracer是一个专为机器人设计的视觉语言模型，旨在通过推理实现空间追踪。</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: normal;\">该项目支持</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: bold;\">多步、基于度量</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: normal;\">的空间追踪，并具备</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: bold;\">显式推理能力</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: normal;\">。RoboTracer不仅保留了其前身RoboRefer的所有功能，还进一步增强了其在复杂场景中的应用能力。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"outline:0px;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;margin-bottom:8px;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"padding:4px;outline:0px;color:rgb(255, 104, 39);letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;text-align:start;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">☆一键收藏：</span></span></p>\n  <p><span style=\"padding:4px;outline:0px;color:rgb(255, 104, 39);letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"padding:4px;outline:0px;color:rgb(255, 104, 39);letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;text-align:start;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><a href=\"https://sota.jiqizhixin.com/project/robotracer\" target=\"_blank\">https://sota.jiqizhixin.com/project/robotracer</a></span></span></span></p>\n  <p><strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">②项目：XR-1</span></span></strong></p>\n  <p><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.5888888888888889\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" data-width=\"1164\" data-height=\"686\" data-imgfileid=\"100017505\" data-aistatus=\"1\" style=\"height: auto !important;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=56fbf68c&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FGU2ibjU7TDkyiaTmZl1iccqPLJBSU7mvbeibnwFpWWoLger2BT6h1ywKDhBaZNFbnqQHJiaeogl8qibvBXOqiatzQxSlQ%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: bold;\">★XR-1是一个多功能且可扩展的视觉-语言-动作框架，支持在不同的机器人体现和环境中进行稳健的多任务学习。</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: normal;\">该项目通过学习统一的视觉-运动表示，旨在实现</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: bold;\">多样化的任务</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: normal;\">和</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: bold;\">环境适应能力</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: normal;\">。XR-1的设计基于Lerobot数据集v2.1，提供了强大的数据加载器，能够无缝读取来自不同来源和体现的数据，支持异构多任务学习和小样本训练。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"outline:0px;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;margin-bottom:8px;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"padding:4px;outline:0px;color:rgb(255, 104, 39);letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;text-align:start;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">☆一键收藏：</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"outline:0px;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;margin-bottom:8px;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"padding:4px;outline:0px;color:rgb(255, 104, 39);letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;text-align:start;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><a href=\"https://sota.jiqizhixin.com/project/xr-1\" target=\"_blank\">https://sota.jiqizhixin.com/project/xr-1</a></span></span></p>\n </body>\n</html>",
  "aiSummary": "本文汇总了 2025 年 12 月 31 日 AI 领域的最新开源项目，包括腾讯 Hunyuan-Motion 1.0、Yuan3.0-Flash、NVIDIA NeMo 以及多个 Agent 和机器人开发项目。",
  "oneSentenceSummary": "本文汇总了 2025 年 12 月 31 日 AI 领域的最新开源项目，包括腾讯 Hunyuan-Motion 1.0、Yuan3.0-Flash、NVIDIA NeMo 以及多个 Agent 和机器人开发项目。",
  "summary": "本文是机器之心 SOTA 模型发布的“今日开源”系列，汇总了 2025 年 12 月 31 日 AI 领域的最新开源进展。内容涵盖了多个重要项目：腾讯 Hunyuan-Motion 1.0 模型，该模型基于 DiT 和流匹配技术，首次将文本到 3D 人类动作生成模型扩展到十亿参数级别；Yuan3.0-Flash，一个采用 MoE 架构的 40B 参数多模态基础模型，通过 RAPO 方法实现“大模型小计算”；NVIDIA NeMo 生成式 AI 框架，专注于大语言模型、多模态和语音 AI；以及 GUI Agent MAI-UI、机器人视觉语言模型 RoboTracer 和多任务机器人框架 XR-1 等。文章简要介绍了每个项目的核心功能和技术亮点，并提供了收录链接，旨在为开发者和研究人员提供快速了解最新 AI 进展的途径。",
